    "body": "Concept ACK, but the reason string isn't wiped on success or between checks. It slightly increases review burden, but having `IsStandardTx` wipe the reason string immediately on entrance is a small reasoning improvement to make sure the string isn't accidentally being kept between calls.\r\n\r\nAFAIK the only \"real\" usage of it is in `src_validation.cpp` mempool checks, so should be easy to verify correctness of change.",
